Class OverrideContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.oddjob.arooa.parsing.OverrideContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ArooaContext
    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class OverrideContext
extends Object
implements ArooaContext
    Wraps an ArooaContext to allow behaviour to be altered. This is a classic application of the Adaptor Pattern.

    rob
